setCountryCode

public void setCountryCode(java.lang.String countryCode)
Sets the country code for the address search. This is optional.
If no country code is specified the search is made:
- on all the available packages, when searching offline
- on entire world on server, when searching online.
Setting a value will help for better results.

Parameters:
countryCode - new country code
